subject: Football
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Time Warner followed Cablevision’s lead Wednesday and said it would not carry the NFL Network on its expanded basic tier during a weeklong free preview that will feature Rutgers in the Texas Bowl on Dec. 28.
